quarterly products, there are any unsold capacities, TSOs may re-allocate the capacity to alternative German connection points. However, this procedure can even work vice versa. If TSOs will observe an auction premium for yearly or quarterly capacity products, unsold capacity shall be re-allocated from one connection point to another to the extent legally or technically possible. <br><br>Capacity conversions according to § 8 (7) (Bundled booking points / conversion of firm unbundled capacity) and according to § 10 (Conversion of interruptible capacity or firm capacities with interruptible elements) of the terms and conditions for the entry and exit contract (entry-exit system) are implemented up to the amount of the smallest value from the new contract, old contract and conversion request (lesser-off rule).<br><br>The following link leads to the information whether or not over-nomination is currently possible at a specific networkpoint:\\n<a href=\\"https://tron-oge.publication.virtimo.cloud\\">UMM-Tool</a><br><br>", "gasType": "HGAS", "direction": "EXIT", "validFrom": "2025-12-09T17:32:55.91+01:00", "categories": ["8ed4e802-9e81-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "8ed4fb6c-9e81-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "8ed4ef1e-9e81-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "8ed4f2b6-9e81-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "8ed4e2e4-9e81-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002"], "congestion": false, "flowUnitId": "5bd05688-9f23-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "adjacentTso": "Fluxys SA", "marketAreaId": "63662dc6-9228-11eb-aa29-06c640c5cd26", "floatingCharge": true, "sellingMethods": ["AUCTION_LONG_TERM", "AUCTION_SHORT_TERM", "SECONDARY_CFO", "SECONDARY_FCFS", "SECONDARY_OTC"], "tradingMarkets": ["PRIMARY", "SECONDARY"], "specificSecondary": false, "networkPointTypeId": "52c09888-9f3b-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002", "specificConditions": [], "undiscountedCharge": false, "ownerOrganisationId": "6e7d8a40-96ea-4fef-a026-fc788b1e7874", "publicAssignedNetworkPointId": "VIP-THE-ZTP-A", "internalAssignedNetworkPointId": "DVGW!?!9870047600001|VIP-THE-ZTP